*****************************************************************************
ATTACHING PROJECT

Just run boincmgr, choose Attach, and follow instructions.
Project URL is boincsimap.org/boincsimap

MANUAL INSTALLATION
 *) If this is your first time in any BOINC project, create a new account at
    http://boincsimap.org/boincsimap/create_account_form.php

 *) Or get your account key at http://boincsimap.org/boincsimap/get_passwd.php

 *) Attach to the project:
    cd %%BOINC_CLIENT_HOME%%
    boinccmd --project_attach boincsimap.org/boincsimap <account key>
*****************************************************************************
